page.title: 17BIOGRAPHY
page.content:
MRS GARNER
Mrs Garner lives at 104 High street Landbeach.Her husband is an antique dealer who collects old items like cars,furniture and paintings.In their house they have lots of antiques.Mrs Garners favourite antique is a old grandfather clock which belonged to a man who lived with Lewis Carol who wrote Alice in Wonderland.Her husband became interested in old things when he was young so when he was older he became involved in antiques.He has been an antique dealer for 20 years.Mr Garner has two repaired cars (Rolls Royce phantom 1 and a Daimler)but the car he realy wants is a Silver Ghost.The Garners have a little farm covering 18 acres,they keep horses and grow crops.
